<h4>Two-day lecture workshop on "Women in Science: A Career in Science" to commemorate Prof. Anna Mani's 96th birthday</h4>
<p>The WiS Panel in collaboration with CMR Institute of Management Studies, Bengaluru organized a 2 day lecture workshop between 22 &amp; 23 August 2014, at CMR Institute of Management Studies, Bengaluru.</p><hr />
